import requests

url = "https://gold-rates-india.p.rapidapi.com/Gold-history/"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "gold-rates-india.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
